Description: This confirms that the error pages are functioning correctly

Suite/Test/Step Name: Test Cases/OTW - HTTPS Redirect - Step 1- Not Logged In - Labs
Test Cases/OTW - HTTPS Redirect - Step 2- Logged In - Labs
Description:
GIVEN I have logged on to the application I am testing 
WHEN I navigate to another OTW application using http rather than https in the URL e.g. http://labs.schoolcomms.com/payments
THEN I am unable to access the screen using HTTP 
AND I am redirected to the same URL on HTTPS e.g https://labs.schoolcomms.com/payments
This test determines the 'remember me' button is working as expected on the Log in screen

Suite/Test/Step Name: Test Cases/POTW - Landing Pages - Step 1 - No payment Subscription landing page
Description:
GIVEN my school does not have a payments subscription
WHEN I log in to POTW
THEN I will be on the No payments subscription landing page
AND I can click the hamburger icon in the corner to navigate to another area OTW

Suite/Test/Step Name: Test Cases/POTW - Landing Pages - Step 2- Create Bank Account Landing Page
Description:
WHEN I log in to POTW 
AND my school does not have a payment request
AND my school does not have an active bank account
AND I have permissions to create bank accounts
THEN I will see the create a bank account landing page

Suite/Test/Step Name: Test Cases/POTW - Landing Pages - Step 3 - No Permission to create bank account landing page
Test Cases/POTW - Landing Pages - Step 4 - Active Payment landing page
Description:
WHEN I log in to POTW and my school has at least 1:
- Active Payment Request
- Future Payment Request
- Expired Payment Request
- Cancelled Payment Request
THEN I will be on the Active Payment landing page AND I will see the other payment request types Future/Expired/Cancelled

Suite/Test/Step Name: Test Cases/POTW - Landing Pages - Step 5 - 0 Active Payment and Other Payment landing page
Description:
WHEN I log in to POTW
AND my school has 0 Active Payment Request and at least 1 of these payment requests:
- Future
- Expired
- Cancelled
THEN i will be on the Future/Expired/Cancelled payment request landing page
AND I will see the options for the other payment request types
AND I will not see the menu for Active Payment requests
AND the payment request is not shown in School Gateway
